Penn Program for Potential Procrastinato.name: Penn Program for Potential Procrastinators
Penn Program for Potential Procrastinato.descr: Ever considered yourself a possible procrastinator, but never actually were able to get the motivation to determine for sure? Then join PPPP, Penn's premier potential procrastinating society! We are seeking unmotivated individuals who, in theory, are interested in joining our group, but can't quite get themselves to start working on our application. Start applying today so that you can procrastinate on the application and ultimately miss the deadline!
